; [AI] ERR -- Microsoft BASIC error trampoline. The word following the CALL is
;      read as the dispatch target: pop it into HL, restore DE/AF, JP (HL).
;      Most callers instead reach an ERR_n entry below via "JP Z,ERR_n+1": the
;      +1 skips the LD BC,$nn1E opcode byte and lands on "LD E,<errcode>", which
;      falls into ERR_26 to print "?<message>" (msg table L_0521) + " in <line>".
